race.comment: Tough way to finish with many converging form lines. MAPLEWAY (2) looks ready to peak third-up after showing nice improvement between his first two runs this campaign. He can settle forward of midfield and blend into the race at the right time. He will take some beating. FLAMBARD (3) comes back from the mile and looks some danger. He maps to get a cosy run and will look the winner at some stage in the straight. Respect Linda Meech's placement of THE DAILY PLANET (7), who makes the trip from Stawell. Expect improvement second-up to 1400m. Both GRINZINGER ACE (12) and GRINZINGER ALLEE (9) can fill the minor money on their best form.
